---
import ContactCTA from '../components/ContactCTA.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About | BlackSword Studio" description="About BlackSword Studio">
	<div class="stack gap-20">
		<main class="wrapper about">
			<Hero
				title="About"
				tagline="Thanks for stopping by. Read below to learn more about Blacksword Studio."
			>
				<img
					width="1553"
					height="873"
					src="/assets/at-work.jpg"
					alt="Jeanine White at work with a colleague"
				/>
			</Hero>

			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Background</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>
						Founded and fully operated by a single independent developer (me), Blacksword Studio was born out of a deep, lifelong love for video games. Without the constraints of large teams or corporate processes, I’m able to focus entirely on the creative core—ensuring every part of the game aligns with the original vision.
					</p>
					<p>
						As the sole creator, I oversee every stage of development: from brainstorming gameplay concepts and writing code to designing levels and polishing visual details. This hands-on approach guarantees the final product carries a distinct, personal touch that reflects genuine passion for game creation.
					</p>
