						Ultrices tincidunt arcu non sodales neque sodales ut. Sed enim ut sem viverra aliquet
						eget sit amet. Lacus luctus accumsan tortor posuere ac ut consequat semper viverra.
						Viverra accumsan in nisl nisi scelerisque eu ultrices. In massa tempor nec feugiat nisl
						pretium fusce.
					</p> -->
				</div>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Design Philosophy</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>At Blacksword Studio, I believe games are more than just entertainment—they are a medium for connection, storytelling, and emotional resonance. My core design philosophy revolves around three key principles:</p>
					<ol>
						<li>Detail-Driven Excellence: It’s the small things that make a game unforgettable. Every menu, every sound effect, and every interaction is crafted with care to create a cohesive, polished experience.</li>
						<li>Uncompromised Creative Vision: Solo development lets me stay true to the game’s core idea without diluting it for mass appeal. The result is a project that feels authentic and unique, not just another generic title.</li>
						<li>Player-Centric Focus: Every design choice is made with the player in mind. Whether it’s intuitive controls, engaging gameplay loops, or a story that resonates, the goal is to put the player’s experience at the forefront.</li>
					</ol>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Contact</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>Email: <a href="mailto:contact@blackswordstudio.com">contact@blackswordstudio.com</a></p>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>

		<ContactCTA />
	</div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.about {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 3.5rem;
	}

	img {
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 1.5rem;
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
	}

	section {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		color: var(--gray-200);
	}

	.section-title {
		grid-column-start: 1;
		font-size: var(--text-xl);
		color: var(--gray-0);
	}

	.content {
		grid-column: 2 / 4;
	}

	.content :global(a) {
		text-decoration: 1px solid underline transparent;
		text-underline-offset: 0.25em;
		transition: text-decoration-color var(--theme-transition);
	}

	.content :global(a:hover),
	.content :global(a:focus) {
		text-decoration-color: currentColor;
	}

	@media (min-width: 50em) {
		.about {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: 1fr 60% 1fr;
		}

		.about > :global(:first-child) {
			grid-column-start: 2;
		}

		section {
			display: contents;
			font-size: var(--text-lg);
		}
	}
</style>
